cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL 

The paper discusses multi-label classification algorithms and their implementation in the MEKA software. This topic falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and specifically deals with classification tasks (cs.IR, cs.AI). The use of pre-processing and problem transformation methods also suggests relevance to natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV) applications.
